{"tid":1598321,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"7:30愛丁堡見 再係咁落去 瓦解呢場運動係香港人自己","createTime":"2019-09-27T11:25:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T14:05:07.000Z","uid":112691,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"9c0a46940b11d2dec5399e3cf2ff0a2a3444e75a","tid":1598321,"uid":112691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T11:25:37.000Z","msg":"日日喺度互屌<br />\n飛機post就打飛機噴到瀉曬<br />\n膠post都上到熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />行動post長期置唔到頂 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">對面藍絲笑緊我地內閧<br />\n笑緊我地係廢青曱甴呀</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">今晚7點半愛丁堡集會 聲援被捕義士<br />\n記唔記得爆眼少女 記唔記得新屋嶺同所有被捕手足？<br />\n賭上自己青春 賭上自己前途<br />\n對唔對得住呢班義士？</span></span><br />\n點解冇人推行動post?<br />\n想再一次認證香港人係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">金魚記憶？</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">10點鳩叫 叫叫下又冇左件事<br />\n跳閘唔跳 罷搭又唔罷 日日互屌同捉鬼</span><br />\n再係咁落去 瓦解呢場運動<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">係香港人自己</span></span><br />\n唔講咁撚多 推爆曬啲行動post<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ONvLyAr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FONvLyAr.jpg&h=3f1dea03&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YcYdHtS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYcYdHtS.jpg&h=d58e921a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iazHAOV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiazHAOV.jpg&h=e5bc0c5c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0viX88X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0viX88X.jpg&h=fbf171b8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qCsYTAE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqCsYTAE.jpg&h=6ad556d4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VJNBFfF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.